Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,444)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能顺带过来真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice of ya to drop in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.93,0:01:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了一样新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I science'd up a new invention
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫做人格赋予机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it the Anthropomorphizer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来为你演示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to demonstrate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seasoning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.87,0:01:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voila
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.99,0:01:26.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速成生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:26.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instant life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.53,0:01:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.68,0:01:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  这真能让东西活起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, can it really bring anything to life?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以赌一把
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can bet the farm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连蟹黄堡都能活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even a krabby patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.45,0:01:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon so
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It lives
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹黄堡活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Krabby Patty lives
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  好怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My, what odd sensations
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel like--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像能感觉了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, like I can feel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是活过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's called livin'
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以走路  可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can walk and talk
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你也满面包经纶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I reckon you got a few thoughts up in the ol' bun too
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon I do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.09,0:02:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的会有蟹黄堡可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real krabby patty who can talk
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.97,0:02:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以让我回话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can talk back to it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以谈论心中所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we can talk about everything we love
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟我从来不知道蟹黄堡爱什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I never knew what krabby patties loved
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在我可以知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but now I can know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且它还可以知道我知道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it can know what I know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我爱蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I know I love krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以带你看我在裤头村的心中所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can show you what I love in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就加倍奶酪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, double my cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为快餐赋予了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I've created life from nothing but fast food
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必我是全世界最聪明的松鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon I'm the smartest squirrel in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:02.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634,244)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我朋友就来这捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's where my friends and I go jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别是你这样的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially new friends like you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还多带了一个小网
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even brought an extra little net
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便你来学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can learn how to--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你捉到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You caught me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drop it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那肮脏的汉堡来路不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know where that nasty patty's been
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那肮脏的汉堡是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That nasty Krabby Patty is my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多加小心  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to be more careful, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是忍不住会好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't help it that you're delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(842,570)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是高菲高伯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Goofy Goober's
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村最美味的冰淇淋店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the tastiest ice cream joint in town
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家表情都好快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks so happy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想跟他们一样快乐  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be happy like them, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是高菲高伯耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a Goofy Goober yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是高菲高伯耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're a Goofy Goober, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个两人份的最快乐的高伯莓黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your happiest Gooberberry Sunrise for two
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.88,0:04:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要我们两个分着吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sharing with ourselves today, are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我要跟我的新朋友分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sharing with my new friend
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  我们还是快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Krabby Patty, we're leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I am never coming back to
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个吃顾客的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a place that would eat a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉大家都要来吃你  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry everyone keeps trying to eat you, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这一生应该就今天最惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be having the worst day of your life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta say
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我并非那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it hasn't been what I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论我跳进别人的嘴里多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I jump in someone's mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们还是不愿意吞了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they still won't swallow me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是故意要跳进别人嘴里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you were jumping into their mouths on purpose?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家不是都想让别人吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everyone want to be eaten?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我不想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想让别人吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to be eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我现在就要让别人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I want to be eaten now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.07,0:05:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.09,0:05:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes I can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1364,750)}托儿所
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看过来  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们已经可以吃固体食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're ready for solid foods
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让你滴上他们的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let them slobber on you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it, moppet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑远点  小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scram, squirt
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My babies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty, come back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,722)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是蟹黄堡到不了我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can't get my hands on a krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我还能圆梦去滑一场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then at least I can go on that ski trip I always wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻子才滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Skiing is for jerks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, krabby patty, over here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要的聊天对象就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a word with
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.38,0:07:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta fit in here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡他非常想要让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty here thinks that he wants to--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想一个人静静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to be alone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.07,0:07:41.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你难道就不想陪着我  当好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:41.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to stay with me and be my friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然想了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是捉水母和冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But jellyfishing and ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只适合你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, they're for people like you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm different
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像你让别人快乐的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like how your purpose is making people happy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是给大家吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by feeding them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让别人快乐的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my purpose is making people happy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是让大家吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by feeding them me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what, Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to help you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变成最棒的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be the best meal you can be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去找最完美的嘴巴来吃掉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's find the perfect mouth to gobble you up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm one happy patty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1382,800)}吃我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.53,0:08:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众们可以进来吃我的蟹黄堡好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Auditions are now open to eat my friend Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next, please
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.32,0:08:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我才会细细品鉴蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only I know how to truly savor a krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  我认为我应该具有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I believe I should have
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把你吃了的完美特质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the distinction of eating you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上一餐品鉴的貌似有点久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you savored that last one a little too long
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I never
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃的小人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a delicious-looking little man
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以嚼你好几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could chew on you for hours
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你嘴巴好像已经塞满东西了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think your mouth is already occupied, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why the long faces?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是黄瓜薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pickle chips
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想让别人吃我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I want is to be eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可就是没法找到完美的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we just can't find the perfect mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许海绵宝宝比较适合把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe SpongeBob could give you the ol' bite and chew
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙口好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舌头健康
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,healthy tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口气清新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minty-fresh breath
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抹番茄酱啊  找到完美的嘴巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spread my ketchup, the perfect mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是我莫大的荣幸  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would be an honor, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是我荣幸才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The honor is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.29,0:10:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡得给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I deserve this patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显我才最饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm clearly the hungriest
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都是为了渺小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All this for little old me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又何必要告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why if you'd told me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我原本只是无生命的配料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I was a lifeless pile of ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某天突然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that someday I'd
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来蟹黄堡的心愿达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I guess it got what it wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以小蜗  好不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Gary, how was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是这松鼠害大家打起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I blame the squirrel for this fracas
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她诱使我们互相攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She made us turn on each other
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手上的邪恶科学害人不浅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with her wicked, wicked science
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.82,0:11:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学就是会有得必有失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, science giveth, and science taketh away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我走吧  科学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me away, science
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:37.17,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF91&\fs160\fsp50}乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(696,678)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(634,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(776,662)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在播出的是电视评论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now with an editorial
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,872)}全员糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here's Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.02,0:11:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人持续不断糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone continues to be horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我为大家证明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I've got the proof
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是我的  每周怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are my "Beefs of the week"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一条怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our first beef is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位肮脏美食家老是先吃后付款
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this filthy foodie always eats before he pays
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃完了就手捧纸钞给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he gives me a handful of money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸钞上面涂满了黏糊糊的油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slathered in slimy grease
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:18.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1650,234)}暂停
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.19,0:12:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对这位烦人精有着十足的怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, do I have a beef with this annoying guy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm done?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还有47条怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I've got 47 more "beefs"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.86,0:12:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来播出的是  乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming up next, it's "Fun-believable"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主持人是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金鱼鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rube Goldfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位还喝奶昔还加芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy puts mustard in his milkshakes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hello, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是金鱼鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Rube Goldfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我们将要探索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and today we'll be exploring
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.82,0:13:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇又未知的裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the amazing and unknown Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1330,256)}乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,830)}金鱼鲁布领衔主演
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们即将会看到的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what you are about to see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.96,0:13:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对能让你们说出  乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is gonna make you say, "That's Fun-believable"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1446,570)}小餐馆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1630,598)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1576,276)}厨师博物馆
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了珊迪的树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here at Sandy Cheeks' Treedome
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, Rube, but
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公厕就在这附近  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The public restroom is right around the corner, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我跟派大星有东西要给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick and I have something to show you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "Fun-believable"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直很想找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just what I'm looking for
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秀出你们的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show us what you got
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think so
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is our chance
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必直接说出来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he still there?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.23,0:13:46.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:46.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's check
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.98,0:13:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  他还在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, he's still there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  等准备好了再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, come back when you are
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是不好意思上镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be camera shy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy do, Rube?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  珊迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Miss Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.00,0:14:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这机械臂感觉不是很乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if the robotic arms weren't "Fun-believable" enough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.10,0:14:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你有什么不为人知的秘密技能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand that you have a secret skill
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that nobody knows about
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.47,0:14:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保持着嘴含最多坚果的松鼠记录
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hold the squirrel record
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the most nuts stored in my cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给大家演示一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you give us a demonstration?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure can
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚好准备了一点榛子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just happened to have some hazelnuts handy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊为天人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像已经没办法另外多塞点坚果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's possible to fit any more than that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好戏还没上场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't seen nuttin' yet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun-believable
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rube?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位观众  看来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, folks, it looks like--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我坚果吃得肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I have a nut-ache
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲁布  得等会儿再回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rube, should we come back later?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  等会儿就等会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, later would be good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来到了诺斯费拉图的古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here at Nosferatu's Castle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里也是裤头村的一座历史地标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which is a Historical landmark
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom, by the way
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks, Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天缘何而来  诺斯费拉图先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why are we here today, Mr. Nosferatu?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我们提示一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you give us a hint?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人想要向你们展示他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master wants to show you his--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,殓锁反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pain-reaction--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  连锁反应机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean chain-reaction machine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.11,0:16:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个怪异机器的工作原理是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So how does this crazy contraption work, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let it roll
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.85,0:16:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snackies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:54.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1058,828)}泡牙
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master says
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲁布的节目由泡牙汽水赞助播出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rube's show is brought to you by Fizzy Fangs Soda
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我牙齿好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tickles my teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.60,0:17:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太乐得不可思议了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fellas, that was truly Fun-believable
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready for you, Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,属于他们的时代大概已经离去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess their moment has passed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在采访的是梅干宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here with "Baby Prunes"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是全裤头村最老的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you're the oldest resident of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么的  警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you, a cop?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  表现好点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ma, behave
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在采访我  玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's interviewing me, Mary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so shut up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are too much
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你早该在七十年前看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey, you should have seen me 70 years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼到中年还放荡不羁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I was middle-aged and wild
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're putting me on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么一个可爱的小老太太怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could a sweet little old lady like you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放荡不羁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever be wild?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人给我立下挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的直升机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy helicopters
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在正飞行在裤头村上空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are flying over Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.55,0:18:22.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,景观尤为壮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:22.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the view is spectacular
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梅干宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baby Prunes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过像你这么大年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone your age
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还这么活蹦乱跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so amazingly active
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还叫活蹦乱跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call this active?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你见识一下活蹦乱跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you active
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梅干太太  可以不用开这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Prunes, you don't have to go this fast
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to impress me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你的机长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your captain speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上又要下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going down again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.41,0:19:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚已经远远不止乐得不可思议了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the furthest thing from Fun-believable
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就让你骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could have fooled me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正前方有会飞的吵东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flapping Yaps at 12:00
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次千船相撞事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This thousand-boat pileup
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.30,0:19:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是全裤头村发生的最惨烈悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,might be the greatest tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ever befall Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想感谢我的太奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I just want to thank my Great Gram-Gram
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天来驾驶直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for flying the copter today
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.05,0:19:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她全裤头村年龄最老  有115岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She is the oldest citizen in Bikini Bottom at 115
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在裤头村才不是最老
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are not the oldest citizen in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才115岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're only 115
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我116岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm 116
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fibber
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我没你老
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't your elder
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就用拳头呼你鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd pop you right in the beezer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最老
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要挑战你  来场直升机决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I challenge you to a copter duel
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开斗吧  跟我助听器一样开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on, like my hearing aid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直升机决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Copter duel?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻频道主持人帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,TV news anchor Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天跳下了一架直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jumped out of a helicopter today
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是禁飞区  姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a no-fly zone, sister
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从我的云上下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of my cloud
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.22,0:20:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最老
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须把这档节目的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to change the name of this show
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从乐得不可思议  改成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from "FUN-believable" to
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ahhh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,714)}手套乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该回家了  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go home, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  刺激的事就点到为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's enough excitement for today
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才最老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the oldest
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来她确实最老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess she was the oldest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:39.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,436)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我现在最老了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm the oldest now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的节目就要告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we've come to end of our show, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想告诉大家  有多么乐得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I just want to tell ya how Fun-be--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了  鲁布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready, Rube
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再不做就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's now or never, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始你们的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it away
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
